In general, the present specimens (
13 females
,
6 males
) correspond well to the descriptions given by Brzeski & Winiszewska-Ślipińska ( 1993 ) and
Andrássy ( 2007 )
. However, a big range in body length was mentioned in both descriptions (Brzeski & Winiszewska-Ślipińska 1993 ;
